      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age or older

          -  alert, able and willing to follow instructions

          -  wheelchair users: patients at the Nova Scotia Rehabilitation Centre

          -  wheelchair users:permission of physician to participate in the study

          -  caregiver:must provide at least part-time wheelchair-handling care for the wheelchair
             user in this study, a minimum of one hour per week on average

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  wheelchair users:suffer from any unstable medical, emotional, or physiological
             conditions that may interfere with participation

